<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạlrãbũ rāʿīã
 falạa yuʿwiz̊nī sẖaẙʾ̊
 yur̊biḍunī marāʿīa
 kẖuḍ̊raⁿạ ại̹lahī ạl̊ḥaỹ̊

[V2]
 2- wamāʾa rāḥaẗiⁿ
 yūridunī ại̹yãạh̊
 yarudũ naf̊sī hādīaⁿạ
 lilsãẙri fī riḍāh̊

[V3]
 3- ại̹n̊ sir̊tu fī ạl̊wādī
 wādī ẓilạali ạl̊maẘt̊
 falạa ạảkẖāfu ạảbadaⁿạ
 ạản̊ta maʿī badaẘt̊

[V4]
 4- ʿukãạzuka ạl̊qawī̃̊
 yā rabũ yaḥ̊mīnī
 ʿaṣāka lī mur̊sẖidaẗuⁿ
 bihā tuʿazĩynī

[V5]
 5- māyỉdaẗa ạl̊hanā
 ratãb̊ta yā karīm̊
 tujāha man̊ ḍāyaqanī
 fāi̹nãka ạlrãḥīm̊

[V6]
 6- biduh̊nika ạlnãqī̃̊
 masaḥ̊ta lī rā̊̉sī
 biniʿ̊maẗiⁿ min̊ka samat̊
 rayãạ gẖadat̊ kā̊̉sī

[V7]
 7- kẖaẙruⁿ waraḥ̊maẗuⁿ
 lī mudãẗa ạl̊ʿum̊ri
 wabaẙtu rabĩy mas̊kanī
 ại̹lay̱ maday̱ ạldãh̊ri</lyrics>
<title>ạlrb rạʿy flạ yʿwznyʾ</title>
</song>